<h2>RESEARCH TOPICS</h2>
<ul>
<li>Large memory sharing systems in loosely coupled workstation 
environments, focusing on Distributed Shared Memory Systems (<!WA10><a href="http://www.cs.ucr.edu/projects/mirage.html">DSM</a>) and 
mobile computing  support using DSM.
<li>Distributed Computing
<li>Operating Systems
<li>Large scale computing systems
<li>Workstation environments
<li>Mobile computing
<li>Reliability and Availability
</ul>
